data.description: Location 2 minutes from schools, shopping and main arteries. Lots of square footage with Primary BR addition to include walk in closet and extra large garage space. Do not drive by and let the double garage door fool you-19 x 33 garage with workbench and heated and cooled. Plenty of space for a shop or craft area and wired for 220. Updated windows and appliances with 3 bath areas. Private yard with covered patio and nice shed. Showing weekdays after 5 and weekends 10-8. One hour notice please. Closing no earlier that mid January. Put this on your show list today!!
